<div class="callout-orange">
<strong>Cost Warning:</strong> The "pass fee to customer" option sounds appealing but can backfire. Adding 6% to displayed prices increases cart abandonment and makes your pricing appear higher than competitors in OTA search results. Most successful operators absorb fees and factor them into base pricing strategy.
