At 500 monthly bookings averaging $75 each, expect FareHarbor costs of $2,000-$3,500 monthly depending on channel mix. At 2,000 monthly bookings, costs scale to $8,000-$14,000+. Compare this to flat-fee alternatives like Peek Pro (around $3,000/month at enterprise tier) or Rezdy (around $1,500/month) to understand the crossover points for your specific operation.

